OL,7,FPC Sharon Beshenivsky's daughter,
OL,8,FLydia, sat down with ITV News' Mary
OL,9,FNightingale almost 20 years after her
OL,10,Fmother was shot and killed while
OL,11,Fresponding to a robbery at a Bradford
OL,12,Ftravel agents
OL,14,FLydia has no memory of her mother, who
OL,15,Fdied when she was just four-years-old.
