OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FFor very many of us, though, that face
OL,8,Fis instantly recognisable. The blonde
OL,9,Fhair and beaming smile of came to
OL,10,Fdominate the headlines, almost 20
OL,11,Fyears ago, after the young police
OL,12,Fconstable was killed responding to a
OL,13,Frobbery at a Bradford Travel agents.
OL,15,FHer colleague Theresa Milburn survived
OL,16,Fher terrible bullet wounds. But Sharon
OL,17,Fdied at the scene - shot at point
OL,18,Fblank range.
OL,20,FShe was just 38-years-old. It was
OL,21,FLydia's fourth birthday.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/13
