OL,7,FSharon had wrapped the presents and
OL,8,Fmade the cake before leaving for work
OL,9,Fthat morning. But she never made it
OL,10,Fhome for the party.
OL,12,FLydia remembers a police car drawing
OL,13,Fup outside, and being excited because
OL,14,Fthat must mean mummy was back to join
OL,15,Fin the fun.
OL,17,FInstead it was two police officers who
OL,18,Fbroke the news to her devastated
OL,19,Ffather. He was determined the party
OL,20,Fshould continue, for Lydia's sake. But
OL,21,Flife had changed forever.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/13
