OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,F'A car pulled up to the top of the
OL,8,Fdrive and I actually thought that it
OL,9,Fwas my mum coming home. Unfortunately,
OL,10,Fit was the police coming to tell my
OL,11,Fdad that she'd been killed.'
OL,13,FThe gang of seven men responsible were
OL,14,Fidentified soon afterwards. Three of
OL,15,Fthem: Mustaf Jama, Yusuf Jama and
OL,16,FMuzzaker Shah were jailed for life.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/13
