OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThree more members of the gang: Faisal
OL,8,FRazzaq, Hassan Razzaq and Raza Ul-Haq
OL,9,FAslam served sentences for robbery and
OL,10,Fmanslaughter. They have all since been
OL,11,Freleased from jail.
OL,13,FThe mastermind behind the raid, Piran
OL,14,FDitta Khan, fled to Pakistan, where he
OL,15,Fevaded capture for many years. He was
OL,16,Ffinally arrested in 2020, and
OL,17,Feventually extradited to Britain to
OL,18,Fface trial.
