OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHe was convicted of Sharon's murder on
OL,8,FApril 4, and he will be sentenced on
OL,9,FMay 10.
OL,11,FI spent the day at home with Lydia -
OL,12,Fnow aged 22 - following the guilty
OL,13,Fverdict.
OL,15,FShe looks startlingly like her late
OL,16,Fmother. The same bright blonde hair
OL,17,Fand distinctive smile. Even the same
OL,18,Finfectious laugh, she's been told,
OL,19,Fthat could silence a room.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/13
