OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThat likeness has brought its own
OL,8,Fchallenges over the years ` combined
OL,9,Fwith the unmistakable surname. There
OL,10,Faren't many Beshenivsky's in Yorkshire.
OL,12,FPeople often say she looks familiar `
OL,13,Fand are mortified once they realise
OL,14,Fwho she is.
OL,16,FSometimes they start to cry,
OL,17,Foverwhelmed by meeting the bereaved
OL,18,Fdaughter of the young policewoman
OL,19,Fwhose death so shocked the nation all
OL,20,Fthose years ago.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/13
