OL,3,C'Tunnel of darkness': Sharon
OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FLydia is fiercely proud of her mother,
OL,8,Fbut I suspect it's sometimes a tough
OL,9,Fburden to bear.
OL,11,FShe openly admits she has struggled
OL,12,Fover the years. Stuck in a "black
OL,13,Ftunnel" of grief, as she puts it. But
OL,14,Fshe feels her mother's presence often,
OL,15,Fand believes Sharon gave a her a "big
OL,16,Fkick" to get herself back on track
OL,17,Fwhen she was at her lowest ebb.
