OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FLydia is now pursuing a career in
OL,8,Fhorses, and holds a responsible
OL,9,Fposition helping to run a racing
OL,10,Fstables. She finds peace in these
OL,11,Fmagnificent creatures, and relishes
OL,12,Fthe tough daily routine of caring for
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,FHorses are completely honest, she
OL,16,Fsays, they don't judge and are a
OL,17,Fwonderful, calm, constant in her life.
OL,19,FOne day she would like to be a mother
OL,20,Fherself, and looks forward to having
OL,21,Fchildren of her own.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/13
