OL,3,C'Tunnel of darkness': Sharon
OL,4,CBeshenivsky's daughter on her mother's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDoes she feel relieved that justice
OL,8,Fhas been done after all this time? Of
OL,9,Fcourse, it's never that simple.
OL,11,FYes, she is delighted that PDK, as she
OL,12,Fcalls him, is behind bars. But she
OL,13,Fhates that he has enjoyed decades of
OL,14,Flife that Sharon was denied.
OL,16,FNow 75-years-old, Ditta Khan will
OL,17,Falmost certainly die in prison.
OL,18,FThere's undoubtedly justice in that
OL,19,Ffor Lydia and her family.
